# Website Structure Cheat Sheet

## Quick Commands

### Start Local Server
```bash
cd music-website
lsof -ti:8000 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null; python3 -m http.server 8000
```
Or use the shortcut:
```bash
serve
```
Then visit: http://localhost:8000

### View Live Site
https://nathanfinkel86.github.io/website/

---

## Git Workflow

### Basic Workflow
```bash
# First, add the changes
git add .

# Then commit
git commit -m "COMMENT HERE"

# Then push
git push origin main
```

### Using the Shortcut
```bash
gc "Your commit message here"
git push
```

### Check Status
```bash
cd "/Users/nathanfinkel/Documents/Admin - Cursor/music-website"
git status                          # Check what's changed
git add .                           # Stage everything
git commit -m "Your message"
git push origin main                # Push to remote
```

### Example: Full Workflow
```bash
git status                          # See what changed
git add .                           # Stage all changes
git commit -m "Refactor: reorganize codebase structure

- Move images to assets/images/ with categories     
- Rename p/ to pages/
- Standardize filenames
- Add .gitignore"
git push origin main                # Push to remote
```

