### Quick Reference: Where to Add Media

| Content Type | File | Section ID | What to Update |
|-------------|------|------------|----------------|
| Ambient audio | `projects.html` | `#ambient` | REPLACE_WITH_AMBIENT_TRACK |
| Glia audio | `projects.html` | `#glia` | REPLACE_WITH_GLIA_TRACK |
| Glia video | `projects.html` | `#glia` | Video placeholder comment |
| Professional video | `projects.html` | `#houseband` | Video placeholder comment |
| Workshop video | `projects.html` | `#facilitation` | Video placeholder comment |
| Morocco audio | `projects.html` | `#morocco` | Audio placeholder comment |
| Music page embeds | `music.html` | Various sections | REPLACE_WITH_*_TRACK |

---

### Troubleshooting

**SoundCloud player not showing?**
- Make sure your track is set to "Public" on SoundCloud
- Check you didn't accidentally delete any other parts of the embed code
- Try a hard refresh (Cmd/Ctrl + Shift + R)

**Video not loading?**
- Check the video is public/unlisted (not private)
- Verify you copied the video ID correctly
- Make sure you closed all HTML tags properly

**Still not working?**
- Check the browser console for errors (F12 → Console tab)
- Make sure your Python server is running (`serve` command)
- Try opening in an incognito/private window to rule out cache issues

