## File Structure

```
music-website/
├── index.html          # Landing page (hero + chips)
├── about.html          # Bio + background
├── projects.html       # Main hub with descriptions + embedded media
├── music.html          # Clean showcase linking back to projects
├── shows.html          # Calendar + recent highlights
├── contact.html        # Form + Instagram
├── assets/
│   ├── styles.css      # All styling
│   ├── site.js         # JavaScript
│   ├── images/
│   │   ├── hero/
│   │   ├── performances/
│   │   └── portraits/
│   └── audio/
└── docs/
    └── Cheat Sheat     # This file!
```

